com.amazonaws.services.iot.client

Class AWSIotConfig

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.amazonaws.services.iot.client.AWSIotConfig

  • public class AWSIotConfig
extends Object
    The class provides default values for the library. All the values defined here can be overridden at runtime through setter functions in AWSIotMqttClient and AWSIotDevice.
